Comment: 0,0:22:20.31,0:23:06.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.91,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.27,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.42,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:19.79,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.82,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:37.18,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.76,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:45.00,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.14,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:52.57,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.29,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In order to reach their next stage, the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:01.66,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the other Straw Hat Pirates have gone to Fishman Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.76,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,located ten thousand meters under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:09.06,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But there, the New Fishman Pirates\Nare planning to overthrow the Ryuuguu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:12.21,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and Vander Decken has been stalking the Mermaid Princess Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.92,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The crew find themselves drawn into these events.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.27,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:14.77,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, who did this to our queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.61,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Find the assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.29,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Find him, look under every rock in the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:24.40,Thoughts,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Ti...  Queen Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:27.46,Thoughts,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:39.92,Thoughts,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I direct my anger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.76,Main,Sniper,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Damn it to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.82,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!  We've found the assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.60,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!  Hurry to the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.27,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Is that him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:58.19,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,He was carrying a gun.  It must be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:58.65,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.61,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.05,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.09,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,We just took him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.83,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:07.82,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.79,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.21,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.38,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.51,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Boss Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.09,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:31.06,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What would become of all of Her Majesty's efforts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.67,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,This would destroy them completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.64,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just too much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.38,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the harsh reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.78,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,No!  He's a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.32,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not he's a pirate is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:53.12,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.28,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.29,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.97,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,A human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:10.72,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,killed our country's queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:18.81,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime's killer was human!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.63,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.70,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,A human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.55,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Her Majesty kept telling us to live with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.97,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,and moved by her words,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:39.04,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,we had decided to walk beside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.50,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,But now a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.19,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,has shattered that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:50.26,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,He's taken the life of the person we all dearly loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:54.76,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,You may be dead, but that doesn't\Ngive us Queen Otohime back, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:07:00.30,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Has this world been forsaken by God and Buddha alike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.19,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,This is too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:07.21,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Far too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.29,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Is His Majesty still inside Koukaku Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.75,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.04,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,It is as you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:32.30,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he couldn't control himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.70,Flashbacks,Guards,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.58,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:44.02,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Don't open it until my bloodthirst passes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.88,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.90,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.72,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:15.25,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit was still carrying a gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:18.06,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,so the soldiers shot him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.62,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,It was a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:25.64,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I would have killed him even if he was unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:32.74,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure Otohime would\Nnever have forgiven me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:37.50,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know when this cycle of revenge started...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:41.45,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,but if I had killed him,\NI'd have just been sucked into that very cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:45.21,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,And any children who saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.83,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,would have the seed of hatred planted in their hearts,\Nso they'd also be dragged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:52.93,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,The cycle would grow even larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:58.42,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,In my head, I understand what Otohime told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:00.97,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather,\NI could if this was happening to someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:09.54,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,But... why can't I kill someone if they kill my wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:14.26,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:21.91,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I lived as a warrior\Nand avenged countless fallen comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:27.46,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Many humans attacked me, and I crushed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:32.80,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,After all that, I didn't think I had the right to help with Otohime's campaign,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.38,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,so I just watched over her instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:40.77,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Why do the innocent die... while I still keep on living?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:48.42,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I tried to continue Otohime's work,\NI would just look like a hypocrite -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:55.66,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,But... peoples' hearts constantly change.\NWe are all full of contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.18,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Both fishmen and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:02.68,Main,Left Minister,0000,0000,0000,,And there will always be things\Nthat only a warrior can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.63,Main,Guards,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.76,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:25.77,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't miss my own wife's funeral -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.42,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father!  Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.94,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:41.62,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.33,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Children...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.20,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:54.43,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me... for not being here when you needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.70,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.96,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:05.81,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I go, letters keep flying after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.98,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fifth one already, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.38,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.59,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi is still only six years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.86,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this Vander Decken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.80,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,He's from a family of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.83,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the children attend the funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.98,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,The assassin might still have\Nsome allies running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:34.08,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,And as for this pirate named Decken,\Ncapture him immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.16,Main,Guards,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.96,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.79,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,The monitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.73,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:23.88,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.43,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.85,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone on Fishman Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:40.69,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I have... something I want to say today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:45.70,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just give me a little of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:52.15,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Just before she died,\Nour mother told us with a smile on her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:56.82,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,that the light of the real sun was just a hair's breadth away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:05.00,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,We have decided to dedicate our lives to fulfilling our mother's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.76,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Princes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:14.43,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Your hearts may not heal\Nin time for the World Council Meeting in two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:19.27,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,but there's another one in six years.  And yet another in ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:26.04,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have conflicted feelings about humans following this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:30.72,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,We discarded all the signatures\Nthat hadn't already burned to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:36.12,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's restart from square one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:45.61,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...\Nwhen everyone's hearts have had time to heal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:52.31,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,let us... dream of the sun together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.93,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,That was ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:25.21,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi, Ryuuboshi and Manboshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:31.56,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Those three, together with the King and Princess,\Nhave been reaching out to the citizens using monitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:35.77,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to their efforts,\Nwe've regathered many of the signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:41.57,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,This is the battle against discrimination\Nthat has been fought on this island for sixteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:46.57,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the reason why the Fishman Pirates\Ndid what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:52.41,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong, the one who caused\Nso much suffering in your homeland,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:57.39,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,was like a little brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:07.48,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning to go after him\Nif he ever tried anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:15.68,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,but Arlong bribed the Navy in the area and made sure that reports of his actions never reached Navy HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:21.19,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, you and many other people had to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.78,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.08,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.58,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.49,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,cut open your stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:41.42,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.17,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,You can apologize with your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:48.00,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,It still wouldn't be enough for me to forgive you,\Nbut at least it might give Nami-san some peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.76,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:54.65,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,But, Nami-san... Think of what they did to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.67,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:16:00.18,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing his story,\Nit's clear that he meant no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.35,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:09.14,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any punishment, if it makes you feel better{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:09.73,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:14.20,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.  Arlong is the one I hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:24.94,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'm glad you're not the mastermind behind the Arlong Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.25,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're Luffy's friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:33.37,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.  I suffered a lot because of the Arlong Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:38.72,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,but in that spiral of pain, I met many good friends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:42.18,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,All of that made me who I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:47.48,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hate you just because you're a fishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:52.86,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,So don't go apologizing for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:58.58,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret it.  I'm having a lot of fun now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.55,Flashbacks,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,So, whoever the culprit is... {Copy-paste from 546}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.91,Flashbacks,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,please don't be angry for me. {End copy-paste from 546}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.85,Flashbacks,Tiger,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the people on our island anything! {Copy-paste from 543}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:19.45,Flashbacks,Tiger,0000,0000,0000,,Not about the tragedy that befell us,\Nnor about our anger toward the humans. {End copy-paste from 543}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:23.45,Flashbacks,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get to you, Jinbe. {Copy-paste from 544}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:27.25,Flashbacks,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,You grew up in the Fishman District together.\NYou're like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:31.29,Flashbacks,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Nyou wouldn't be able to kill him.{End copy-paste from 544}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:42.04,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve such kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.54,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I am in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:53.42,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nyuu- Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.56,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jinbe-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.96,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,I totally understand\Nhow tough it must be for you, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.98,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real man, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:15.36,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger... Otohime... I love you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.49,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.37,Thoughts,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,He was suffering so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.37,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.61,Main,Crew,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.42,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:47.29,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I sure slept well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:51.34,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, I thought you were\Nactually paying attention for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.56,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.79,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:00.02,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What, I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.37,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.83,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, be quiet!  I told you, I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:10.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:13.55,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So, Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.45,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the robber that Wimp's mom caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:19.92,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep through the whole thing?!\NThat was the opening of the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:20.96,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.17,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:26.00,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,You there... Your name is Shirahoshi, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:30.14,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami-chin!  She's royalty!\NYou can't just address her as "You"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.71,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:36.73,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.\NRemembering my mother made me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.53,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,She sounded like a wonderful mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.41,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:46.11,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Nami-chin-sama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.26,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!  Nami-chin is just her nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.33,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,The -chin isn't actually part of her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:58.92,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've met you,\Nbut it feels like I've known you since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.80,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:05.72,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  Maybe it's because our circumstances are kind of similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:12.31,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, sorry for taking so much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:18.53,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,First, we have to find out what's happening\Nat Ryuuguu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:25.10,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Hody and his crew attacked.\NHis Majesty and the guards have been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:29.45,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Four of your companions are missing, and we don't know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.28,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the information we have at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:34.33,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nyuu- Jinbe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:41.09,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If things are going according to Hody's plan, even worse things are happening around the country now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:46.14,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You know what Hody is planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:52.52,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I always suspected that he was planning something in the Fishman District after leaving the army...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:56.60,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,but he never gave me an opportunity to find out what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.82,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:04.28,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hody hates humans even more than Arlong-san does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:11.49,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he's grown up by feeding on the anger and hatred of the fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:17.17,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But, he's clearly different from Arlong-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:24.13,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san looked down on humans,\Nbut he'd never hurt his fellow fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.88,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But with Hody...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.85,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're just a fishman who wants to live in peace with humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.57,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,he will mercilessly attack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:40.15,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The World Council Meeting only takes place every four years and will happen this year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:43.19,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We've gathered a lot of signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:47.41,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This was going to be the year when\NKing Neptune finally let the world know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:51.21,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,that Fishman Island wants to emigrate to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.54,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.41,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Hody wants to prevent that from happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:22:00.34,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, even more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.43,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:14.22,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,A gigantic Snail Phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:15.77,Main,Den,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:18.30,Main,Den,0000,0000,0000,,A Projector Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:19.95,Main,Den,0000,0000,0000,,What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.37,0:22:25.64,Main,Den,0000,0000,0000,,Look!  The monitor is turning on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:28.33,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,It's projecting something onto the bubble layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.21,0:22:32.33,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:36.70,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:40.00,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, you know that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:42.84,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nyuu- Hody...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:45.18,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  That's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:45.91,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Hacchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:51.34,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,To all citizens of Fishman Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:53.38,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:59.98,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I am the captain of the New Fishman Pirates,\Nfrom the Fishman District...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.25,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Hody Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:10.11,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Hody's ambitions are broadcast to the whole of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:16.87,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shocking plan to destroy Ryuuguu Kingdom, and make himself the new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:20.25,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Fishman Island are extremely upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:25.92,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,but Hody has another announcement\Nthat causes even greater fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.13,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.59,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,A Great Shock to the Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:30.84,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Orders to Execute Neptune
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.77,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
